# The library and workload images COPY only main.libsonnet + lib/ and one
# workloads/<name>/ dir, so nothing else belongs in the build context. vendor/ is
# the important exclusion: the e2e scenarios symlink vendor/github.com/metio/kurly
# back to the repo root (so jsonnet resolves kurly's canonical path), and taring
# that self-referential symlink into the context would loop.
vendor/
.git/
docs/
node_modules/
